::Battera::

She stood there feeling rather silly. She looked at Rex and felt her 
face flush again.  "I...ah..I'm sorry if I got in the way earlier.  I 
just wanted to help."  She looked up and saw the other bot standing 
there. "I see you have company. I'll let you to it." She turned and 
walked to her door.
